sly and securely.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"3691\" data-end=\"4183\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"3691\" data-end=\"3865\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3693\" data-end=\"3726\"><strong data-start=\"3693\" data-end=\"3724\">Out-of-the-box plugin setup<\/strong>:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"3729\" data-end=\"3865\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"3729\" data-end=\"3755\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3731\" data-end=\"3755\">E-commerce (WooCommerce)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"3758\" data-end=\"3775\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3760\" data-end=\"3775\">Booking systems<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"3778\" data-end=\"3805\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3780\" data-end=\"3805\">CRMs like HubSpot or Zoho<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"3808\" data-end=\"3862\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3810\" data-end=\"3862\">Live chat integrations (Tawk.to, WhatsApp, Intercom)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"3866\" data-end=\"4012\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3868\" data-end=\"3899\"><strong data-start=\"3868\" data-end=\"3897\">Custom plugin development<\/strong>:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"3902\" data-end=\"4012\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"3902\" data-end=\"3956\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3904\" data-end=\"3956\">Tailor-made features for your workflows or reporting<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"3959\" data-end=\"4012\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3961\" data-end=\"4012\">Custom post types, dashboards, or role-based access<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"4013\" data-end=\"4183\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"4015\" data-end=\"4035\"><strong data-start=\"4015\" data-end=\"4034\">Advanced setups<\/strong>:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"4038\" data-end=\"4183\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"4038\" data-end=\"4084\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"4040\" data-end=\"4084\">Multilingual websites (WPML, TranslatePress)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"4087\" data-end=\"4122\">\n<p class=\"\" da