\"996\" data-end=\"1147\"><strong data-start=\"996\" data-end=\"1021\">Responsive by default<\/strong> \u2013 All layouts are tested across modern browsers and devices to guarantee a flawless experience on desktop, tablet and mobile.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1148\" data-end=\"1293\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1150\" data-end=\"1293\"><strong data-start=\"1150\" data-end=\"1180\">Designed for accessibility<\/strong> \u2013 We adhere to WCAG standards to ensure users with visual or physical impairments can easily navigate your site.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<blockquote data-start=\"1295\" data-end=\"1452\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1297\" data-end=\"1452\">Whether you\u2019re a government agency with strict brand controls or an NGO that needs multilingual support, we design with flexibility and compliance in mind.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1454\" data-end=\"1484\"><strong data-start=\"1458\" data-end=\"1484\">SEO-First Architecture<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1486\" data-end=\"1644\">Every website we build follows <strong data-start=\"1517\" data-end=\"1539\">SEO best practices<\/strong> at a technical level. We don\u2019t just install an SEO plugin\u2014we optimise every element for discoverability.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1646\" data-end=\"2052\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1646\" data-end=\"1710\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1648\" data-end=\"1710\"><strong data-start=\"1648\" data-end=\"1672\">Clean, semantic code<\/strong> with proper heading structure (H1\u2013H6)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1711\" data-end=\"1811\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1713\" data-end=\"1811\"><strong data-start=\"1713\" data-end=\"1730\">Schema markup<\/strong> for enhanced search engine visibility (e.g., articles, FAQs, products, services)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1812\" data-end=\"1871\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1814\" data-end=\"1871\"><strong data-start=\"1814\" data-end=\"1830\">XML sitemaps<\/strong>, robots.txt, and canonical tags included<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1872\" data-end=\"1952\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1874\" data-end=\"1952\"><strong data-start=\"1874\" data-end=\"1906\">Core Web Vitals optimisation<\/strong> to improve Google ranking and user experience<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1953\" data-end=\"2052\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1955\" data-end=\"2052\">Pre-installed and configured <strong data-start=\"1984\" data-end=\"1997\">SEO tools<\/strong> like Rank Math or Yoast for on-page content management<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2054\" data-end=\"2144\">We build with search in mind from day one, helping your site stand out in crowded markets.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2146\" data-end=\"2176\"><strong data-start=\"2150\" data-end=\"2176\">Performance &amp; Security<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2178\" data-end=\"2331\">Speed and security are non-negotiable for any organisation operating online. We implement proven performance and protection measures across all projects:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2333\" data-end=\"2773\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2333\" data-end=\"2507\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2335\" data-end=\"2352\"><strong data-start=\"2335\" data-end=\"2350\">Performance<\/strong>:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2355\" data-end=\"2507\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2355\" data-end=\"2393\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2357\" data-end=\"2393\">Caching (server-side + plugin-based)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2396\" data-end=\"2439\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2398\" data-end=\"2439\">CSS\/JS minification and image compression<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2442\" data-end=\"2507\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2444\" data-end=\"2507\">CDN integration (e.g., Cloudflare) to improve global load times<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2509\" data-end=\"2773\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2511\" data-end=\"2524\"><strong data-start=\"2511\" data-end=\"2523\">Security<\/strong>:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2527\" data-end=\"2773\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2527\" data-end=\"2579\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2529\" data-end=\"2579\">SSL certificate installation and HTTPS enforcement<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2582\" data-end=\"2620\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2584\" data-end=\"2620\">Web Application Firewall (WAF) setup<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2623\" data-end=\"2675\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2625\" data-end=\"2675\">Malware protection and regular vulnerability scans<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2678\" data-end=\"2715\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2680\" data-end=\"2715\">Daily or weekly <strong data-start=\"2696\" data-end=\"2715\">offsite backups<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2718\" data-end=\"2773\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2720\" data-end=\"2773\"><strong data-start=\"2720\" data-end=\"2741\">Uptime monitoring<\/strong> to alert our team of any issues<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2775\" data-end=\"2887\">We follow strict WordPress hardening protocols and ensure your site is protected against common vulnerabilities.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2889\" data-end=\"2922\"><strong data-start=\"2893\" data-end=\"2922\">CMS Training and Handover<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2924\" data-end=\"3079\">We believe in empowering our clients. Once your site is live, we provide full training and documentation to help your internal teams manage it confidently.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"3081\" data-end=\"3441\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"3081\" data-end=\"3170\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3083\" data-end=\"3170\"><strong data-start=\"3083\" data-end=\"3116\">User-friendly dashboard setup<\/strong> \u2013 Customised admin panel with only the tools you need<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"3171\" data-end=\"3287\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start